> > > > > - Texian's  Personal Hygiene -
> > > > >
> > > > > If you have to vacuum the bed, it's time to change  the
> > > > > sheets.
> > > > >
> > > > > Plucking  unwanted nose hair is time-consuming work.  A
> > > > > cigarette  lighter and a small tolerance for  pain  can
